        <font color="white" face="Verdana" size="2"> OK, today i dinged 51, so i figured, now im a badass iksar necro, and i can go take down some guys ive been looking at solo, and get myself some nice resist gear, and maybe some cash so i can buy shoes, as im barefoot.   Well, i look on alakazam and see that soothsayer dregzak drops some nice items.  a 10svm earring i could use, a 2 int shoulder item i could use, and a nice druid bracer that i could offer to sell only for an outrageously high price to a dr00d.  <BR>So, looking at my map from eqatlas, i head down to raise some hell... I go around the place invised, and I decide that the best place to make a pet and buff up is right between room 1 and 2 on the map, which is the pool room, and dregzaks room.  Now, at this point, i have on every piece of resist gear i own, ad i have resist cold, magic, disease, and dmf on.  almost every resist at 130 or so. Also diamondskin is up.  Now, i start to cast up a pet, and i get aggroed like there is no tomorrow.  I dont know if these goblins were all on the CB radio or what, but there were goblins charging in at me fast, and they were pissed.  ok, somehow, i channel thru the beating, and make a pet, now at this point, there are at least 6 goblins on me, in a small room, and i figure, if i move, i will aggro more, and also, will be closer to the spawn point<BR>SO, after about 3 secs, i FD, pet lasts about 2 secs longer, poor fella.  Now, FD works, the gobbies leave, and here i am.  alone.  ok, i have about 500hps left, so i start to think what to do.  No plan comes to mind, other than wait to full life and try to stand up and use my POST-nerf CoS...pre nerf would have saved me.  when i do, 4 gobs rush me, interrupt my first FD, and kill me with a cast after my second works.  <BR>my question is this. is there a safe place closeby to make a pet and hast him , then single pull these guys?<BR>ALso, is this a case of casters being buffed as hell after the last patch? cause they were all lt ble and green to me and i got nuked ALOT.  after the first FD, when i stood, i counted 6 nukes for 206 max.  That seems kinda high considering the level difference and my resists.  i didnt completely resist a single nuke.<BR>Does anyone have any experience with these bastards and could throw me a few tips? cause im definately gonna pay these SOB's back.</P><P>Also, i now understand the power of the pre-nerf CoS, lol....if anyone wants to sell one on Karana, gimme a tell in game, or on here.Im broke now, but ill farm the cash.</P><P> </font></td>

