         pool room has the worst pathing in the zone, you can and will get chain agro trying to do anything in there at full spawn.</P><P>Only way to safely clear it is to start at that aforementioned secret wall and work the long way around that tunnel that goes behind the area.</P><P>Snare everything and keep tight control on your pet, turn taunt off. Your pet can and will agro everything in the region if you let him.</P><P><BR><a href="http://tru7h.org/absor/" target="_blank">http://tru7h.org/absor/</a> -  ask absor anything!<BR><a href="http://xzzy.org/ereet/" target="_blank">http://xzzy.org/ereet/</a><a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
