        <hr noshade size="2" color="#545A7D">
        
         Oh, the other thing that often causes problems are the pets of the various gobbies in that area. Lets say you get a fanatic, who has a skelly pet up. You pull the gobbie with darkness, the pet charges at you. You back up to your pet and get your pet to attack the other pet. Meanwhile, because you backed up, the fanatic took a strange path to get to you. Well, the hate list on a pet transfers to its owner, and because your pet would be on the hate list of the fanatic's pet, the fanatic will bring a pile of adds back at you.</P><P>Cheers,<BR>Ancagalon the Black<BR>Warlock - Terris Thule</P><P> <a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
