         If I were you I'd just make a pet at the zone in and work my way down there killing every gobbo in your way. (Keep the salts and skins that drop since it will help you in getting Chardok faction which will get you a really nice ring down the road a bit.)</P><P>Another good thing to do would be to find a level 40-45 cleric and have him come along with you to heal and buff your pet. If he's grouped with you he will make some serious exp. (12% exp bonus in that dungeon.) That will help you clear the whole dungeon and make a cleric very happy. ;)</P><P></P><P><img src="http://www.jackntracie.com/images/gojirax.jpg" border=0><a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
